{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "变成小孩子模样的兰扎卜\\n和洛依泽以及变成人类模样的\\n墨丘利成功潜入学院。\\n等待他们的是秘密任务、激烈对决，\\n以及意想不到的浪漫故事！"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "学生",
            "context": "新来的老师\\n真是大美人啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "学生",
            "context": "而且还是龙，真帅气！\\n啊……老师来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110385_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "大家请安静。\\n今天要向大家介绍\\n两位转校生。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110385_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "一位是兰扎卜同学。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "嗨，请多关照！\\n以后大家一起玩吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110385_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "还有一位是洛依泽同学。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "我擅长做家务，\\n喜欢照顾人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "缺点也许就是保护欲过度吧……\\n请大家多多关照！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110385_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "大家要好好和他们相处哦。\\n你们两位就坐在……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110385_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "课间",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "总算成功潜入了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "是啊，不过这才刚开始呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "是啊，我们得收集\\n这个学院的情报才行，\\n要怎么做……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "男孩",
            "context": "洛依泽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "哎呀，你是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "我叫阿隆，是你的同班同学……\\n但现在不是了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "诶？什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "我喜欢你，从今天开始\\n请做我的恋人吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "诶！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哎哟喂♪\\n洛依泽～很受欢迎嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "别开我玩笑好不好！\\n那个，这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "抱、抱歉，\\n我不能做你的恋人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "诶！？为什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "你问为什么……\\n我们才刚认识啊，\\n也不了解对方……对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你跟一个小鬼认真\\n回答个什么劲啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "正因为对方是孩子，才不能小看。\\n以大人的态度真诚回答，\\n也算是为他的将来好。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "原来如此，\\n不愧是有育儿经验的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "就算你不了解我，\\n我也了解你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "我的第六感告诉我，\\n你是个姐姐！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "姐、姐姐？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "真实身份暴露了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "怎、怎么可能……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "我们明明一样大，但你却有\\n满满的包容力！还擅长照顾人！\\n和一般的那些女生不一样！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "我想让你牵着我的手！\\n摸我的头！把你的腿\\n给我当枕头！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "这种心情，正是爱！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不，这是哪门子的爱啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "哼！你这个转校生！\\n要对我的爱指手画脚吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "倒也不是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "我知道了！\\n你也喜欢洛依泽吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "所以才对我的爱吹毛求疵！\\n你是我的情敌吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不不，为啥会变成这样！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "哼，好吧。转校生，\\n来跟我一决高下吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "看我们谁配得上洛依泽！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "开启火热恋爱对决的钟声\\n响彻了整个学院——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "不，这只是上课铃而已……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120080_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "狄涅尔士兵",
            "context": "今天要在户外进行战斗演练！\\n大家要为了帝国拼命努力！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "战斗演练……\\n竟然还有这种课。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "而且还是以帝国兵\\n和魔兽为对手，\\n这种演练也太过分了吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "虽说现在这世道，\\n是掌握一些防身术比较好……\\n但也够动真格的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "有这种课程就意味着\\n他们在这里培养这些孩子，\\n最终是为了充军吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "可也不光是让他们学习\\n使用兵器，有时候也会悠闲地\\n讲授一些书本知识……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "有破绽！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好痛啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "你小子！干嘛啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "当然是比试啦。\\n我们来比一比谁才是\\n配得上洛依泽的男人吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "首先，在这次演练中\\n打倒更多魔兽的人获胜！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120097_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "阿隆",
            "context": "不过，反正你也\\n赢不过我的爱！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那个混蛋……\\n都找上门来了可别怪我不客气！\\n这就是成熟男人的做派。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_10"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "让大哥哥我教教你\\n什么是懂礼貌。给我站住！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "啊，我说兰扎卜！\\n跑掉了……哪里成熟了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "照这个样子下去，\\n在身体变回原形之前\\n真的能收集到情报吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "早熟的女生",
            "context": "那么……\\n小洛你选哪个呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "什、什么选哪个？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "早熟的女生",
            "context": "别害羞嘛～还能是什么啊～\\n当然是指阿隆和兰扎卜\\n你喜欢哪个嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "早熟的女生",
            "context": "我选阿隆～他头脑聪明，\\n而且我喜欢长相清爽的♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "早熟的女生",
            "context": "我肯定选兰扎卜！\\n不觉得他将来一定\\n是那种肌肉硬汉吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "早熟的女生",
            "context": "啊～我懂！\\n肌肉硬汉至上啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110256_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "洛依泽",
            "context": "（肌肉硬汉至上？\\n现在的小姑娘好这口？）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "早熟的女生",
            "context": "真羡慕小洛啊～有机会玩\\n“你们别为我吵了！”\\n那一套～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_22211_02_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "早熟的女生",
            "context": "是啊～有一种\\n学院浪漫爱情活动\\n正火热进行中的感觉～",
